{"tid":1244713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"621監察記錄重要性","createTime":"2019-06-20T04:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T08:18:31.000Z","uid":265814,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"90f34f76595c2a0b3d3873417ed8dc83ce6bbe4a","tid":1244713,"uid":265814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:50:24.000Z","msg":"睇完呢兩日既記者會/比加超出黎既答問<br />\n我自己覺得620既死線就唔多樂觀<br />\n621出去既人除左要有gear去保護自己之外<br />\n最好可以有多D監察既工具黎保做證具去保護自己<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有Drone(航拍機）就keep住唔同角度去拍低重要既時刻</strong></span> （盡量唔好飛黎飛去，所以多幾部先有用）<br />\n因為有時新聞/LIVE都未勿可以睇到成個大環境<br />\n有山狗/GoPro既最好可以俾最前排既人帶住<br />\n有鏡頭影住速龍都怯一怯啦 （雖然佢地身上應該都冇咩number喇）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mgNjJSu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmgNjJSu.png&h=2d5a40ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n------------<br />\n想問下各位意見<br />\n除左學生，其實有班中女/人地阿媽，呢啲女人仔既角色都想支持學生<br />\n但又唔係勇武，去唔到前線，有冇咩野可以俾到佢地幫手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b4403f6fde81e79ceddc3e5ddf05830d0f178b","tid":1244713,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:06:33.000Z","msg":"621 醜事傳千里，輿論救義士。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1244725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1244725</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n新部署，入嚟討論"},{"pid":"a20cfab870926ad51ff2c9676ac27e5c5245954e","tid":1244713,"uid":28870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好再問我點解要衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/crGMpHH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcrGMpHH.jpg&h=4ff620ad&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n要做的事好簡單 6月21 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\